            "body_html": "<p>A power-packed component bundle that includes every feature of the Gantt, Scheduler, Scheduler Pro, Grid, Calendar and TaskBoard. Excellent value for apps drawing on more than one Bryntum product.</p>",
            "body_text": "A power-packed component bundle that includes every feature of the Gantt, Scheduler, Scheduler Pro, Grid, Calendar and TaskBoard. Excellent value for apps drawing on more than one Bryntum product.",
