            "eyebrow": "Gantt Chart",
            "heading": "Feature-Packed Gantt Chart",
            "body_html": "<p>Our Gantt chart is the most capable JavaScript Gantt component on the market. A wide-reaching API and a vast feature set together cover every project-management need you have. Written in pure JavaScript / TypeScript, it drops cleanly into any React, Angular or Vue app.</p>",
            "body_text": "Our Gantt chart is the most capable JavaScript Gantt component on the market. A wide-reaching API and a vast feature set together cover every project-management need you have. Written in pure JavaScript / TypeScript, it drops cleanly into any React, Angular or Vue app.",
