            "heading": "Tailorable Calendar",
            "body_html": "<p>Our contemporary Calendar component delivers a complete calendar toolkit with day, week, month, year and agenda views. It ships with a set of polished widgets too: filters, an event editor, a month navigation bar and more.</p>",
            "body_text": "Our contemporary Calendar component delivers a complete calendar toolkit with day, week, month, year and agenda views. It ships with a set of polished widgets too: filters, an event editor, a month navigation bar and more.",
