            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Task Board",
            "heading": "Kanban Task Board Component",
            "body_html": "<p>Our contemporary JS Kanban Task Board web component makes it easy to keep on top of day-to-day work. It supports swimlanes and lets you drag tasks across columns. A handful of config lines is enough to match your workflow with any number of columns &amp; swimlanes.</p>",
            "body_text": "Our contemporary JS Kanban Task Board web component makes it easy to keep on top of day-to-day work. It supports swimlanes and lets you drag tasks across columns. A handful of config lines is enough to match your workflow with any number of columns & swimlanes.",
